		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>March 25 5622&#47;1862</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir &#38; <hi rend="underline">Colleague</hi>&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">The above address<lb/> will no doubt excite your curiosity &#38; astonishment<lb/> I will at once gratify both.  After 4 months&#39;<lb/> reflection &#38; upon the most urgent solicitations of<lb/> my friends &#38; the congregation itself&#44; I have accepted<lb/> the <hi rend="underline">unanimous</hi> election&#44; or rather <hi rend="underline">invitation</hi> &#40;for<lb/> I did not apply for the place&#41; as Minister<lb/> of the congregation <hi rend="underline">Anche&#45;Emeth</hi> at <placeName>Albany</placeName>&#44;<lb/> formerly <persName>Dr Wise&#39;s</persName> congregation.  What do you<lb/> say to this&#44; that <persName>Dr. W.</persName> must see me at the<lb/> head of his former flock&#63;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As I intend <add>Hebrew</add> to<lb/> enter upon my duties a fortnight hence&#44; and<lb/> shall&#44; in consequence&#44; be more than occupied<lb/> with winding up my business here and<lb/> preparing for my removal&#44; it will be im&#45;<lb/>possible for me to continue&#44; for the next 2<lb/> months&#44; my translation for the <hi rend="underline">Occident</hi>&#59; but<lb/> rely upon it&#44; as soon as I shall be comfortably<lb/> settled&#44; I shall recommence&#44; &#38; finish the work<lb/> without interruption.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As to my future course in the holy<lb/> office upon which I am about to <hi rend="underline">re</hi>&#45;enter&#44;<lb/> I will say nothing&#59; you know my views&#44;<lb/> principles &#38; convictions&#8212;the cause of<lb/> the Jews &#38; Judaism shall never suffer<lb/> shame &#38; disgrace at my hand&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Believe me to remain&#44; as ever&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Yours &#38;c</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">M Mayer</persName></p>
			
